fields.title: The Dark Knight
fields.review: One of the best film i have ever watched with a very interesting character stories.

fields.title: Gladiator
fields.review: Great movie with instane cinematography techniques.

fields.title: Titanic
fields.review: A classic of a film with a legendary love story. The actors did an amazing job potraying their own characters.

fields.title: Mencuri Raden Saleh
fields.review: Great Indonesian heist movie with a few flaws but perfect for a first one. Amazing acting by the actors.

fields.title: Pengabdi Setan
fields.review: A good Indonesian horror film which offers a unique horror experience. Interesting stories with twists at the end.

fields.title: Avatar
fields.review: Brilliant film whcih is worthy of the record they hold of having the most movie sales worldwide.

fields.title: Justice League
fields.review: A flawed movie with too much plot holes but very enjoyable for long time fan of the series who are excited to see their heroes on the big screen.

fields.title: Deadpool
fields.review: One of the best anti-hero movies which is very funny, entertaining, and refreshing.

fields.title: The Truman Show
fields.review: A very great film which makes you think that the story relates to you very much in real life. The movie offers new perspective on life.
A very iconic film with its flaws but very faithful to the comic series of the name.
